name: Hattori Hanzo's Timetravel miss
description:
n order to eradicate the source of the dragons, Hattori Hanzo has been traveling through other worlds and parallel universes using an evolutionary time machine to find the world where the dragons lived.

One day, Hanzo makes a mistake.

I reversed the x-axis and z-axis of the coordinates that I input into the time machine.

The time travel was carried out.
I arrived at a place in the depths of the ocean where I did not know when or where.
All I know is that it's probably Earth.

Hanzo quickly throws the time machine and returns to the world he came from.

You can reading more storys on our WEBSITE [tezosninjas.xyz]
